{"word":"G550 - ἀπειπόμην - apeipómēn - ap-i-pom'-ane - Renounce","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπειπόμην</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apeipómēn</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-i-pom'-ane</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Renounce</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வெறு"},{"paragraph":"1. to speak out, set forth, declare"},{"paragraph":"2. to forbid"},{"paragraph":"3. to give up, renounce"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Reflexive past of a compound of <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G2036 - ἔπω - épō - ep'-o/2036\">G2036</a>; to <i>say off</i> for oneself, that is, <i>disown:</i> - renounce.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}